        "rest_url": "https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-json/tribe/events/v1/events/31603",
        "title": "Living History: From the Rock Wall",
        "description": "<p><span data-teams=\"true\">In celebration of Black History Month, we are collaborating with the Marian Cheek Jackson Center for the 3rd year to share the stories of Chapel Hill and Carrboro&#8217;s Black history. The Marian Cheek Jackson Center is a public history non-profit that works to honor the legacy of historic Black neighborhoods, Black history, and advocate for housing justice.<br />\nLearn local history through the voices of local poets, speakers, and historians. This free event invites you to explore the legacy and impact of the historic Northside, Pine Knolls, and Tin Top neighborhoods, offering personal narratives from significant moments in local history. Come sample food from local Black-owned businesses whose products we carry at our stores. Everyone is welcome to join us in this meaningful celebration!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-31605\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-300x300.png 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-150x150.png 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-768x768.png 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-200x200.png 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-600x600.png 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1-100x100.png 100w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-1.png 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-31607\" srcset=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-300x300.png 300w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-150x150.png 150w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-768x768.png 768w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-200x200.png 200w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-600x600.png 600w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3-100x100.png 100w, https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-3.png 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-2.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Living-History-From-the-Rock-Wall-2026-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=